txt.en: You have encountered a band of Wargs led by Warmaster Bugud patrolling the eastern plains of the Sutcrofts.
With Bugud and his bloodthirsty Wargs defeated, the Free Peoples of the Sutcrofts can live free of the fear of such a fearsome enemy.
You have discovered a savage Orc Warg-rider and his two Warg guardians on the eastern plains of the Sutcrofts. Such a grave threat to the Free Peoples must be eliminated.
You have discovered a band of Wargs led by a savage Orc rider patrolling the eastern plains of the Sutcrofts.
Bugud can be found roaming the crofts outside Snowbourn with his warband.
